				      <span>Labor Intensive</span>
				  </h1>
				<h2>By  <a class="author" title="Posts by Anastasia Lukianchikov" href="//dailybruin.com/author/anastasia-lukianchikov/" rel="author">
					Anastasia Lukianchikov</a></h2>
